INSERT INTO PageSearchIndex VALUES(1,' Bidding Pond: Bidding Pond was the first website to auction off merchandise for bitcoins. It is essentially the eBay of bitcoins.   Bitcoin Classifieds: A leader in online ads where you can find merchandise for sale for bitcoins.   Bitcoin World Market: Bitcoin world market is perhaps the largest bitcoin store. Check out their large selection of unique merchandise.  There are many great websites for finding merchandise in the bitcoin community. Here are just a few. &nbsp; \r\nSearch Bitcoin is committed to helping people discover merchandise and services available in the bitcoin community. \r\nOur database is comprehensive, and includes every item for sale in nearly every store.  ','Home','',NULL,'2011-06-24 22:52:00','2011-09-30 13:40:56',NULL)
