 ,(126,' Several people in the bitcoin community informed us that our homepage was confusing to figure out for first time users. This prompted us to redesign some of the menus. We think that the changes we\'ve made make the hompepage easier to use. Here are some of the changes: \r\n &nbsp; \r\n\r\nWith just one mouse click you can now visit the store selling merchandise seen on our homepage.\r\nYou can now leave comments and reviews about any bitcoin store that you have had experience with so that other people may see what you wrote before buying.\r\nVendors can now subscribe to their store\'s reviews, so that they can see what people are writing about their business.\r\n\r\n We are always trying to improve our website. If you have any feedback then leave us a comment below or contact us here.  ','Testing New UI Design','We at Search Bitcoin are always trying to improve our service. That is why we have redesigned some of the menus on our homepage to make our site easier to navigate. You can now even write reviews about the different bitcoin stores.','/blog/testing-new-ui-design','2011-10-03 09:13:00','2011-10-03 09:28:34',NULL)
 ,(76,'We are committed to the development of a Bitcoin Chamber of Commerce. To that end we are offering our entire database of all the businesses we have found that accept bitcoins.  Bitsites: Bitsites is the equivalent of Yelp for the bitcoin community. We are currently in the process of sharing our database of bitcoin businesses with them.  There are many great websites where you can find other bitcoins businesses. Here are a few of them.  If you would like access to the database then please use the contact us page to place a request. We are happy to share our database, and there will be no charge. However, this is a community driven project, and as such you will have to give back. If you operate a competing directory listing service, you will have to share any additional enteries into the database with the rest of the community. In this manner, the entire bitcoin community can benefit.&nbsp;We will also be happy to include a link to other websites that provide an online directory listings of bitcoin business and services.   Search Bitcoin is searching the web to find businesses that accept bitcoins. This has put us in the unique position to help consumers and other businesses find the products and services they need from the bitcoin community. To help foster the development of the bitcoin economy, we will be releasing our entire database of bitcoin businesses that we have found. \r\n But we need your help! If you own a business and would like to or already accept bitcoins as a method of payment then we want to hear from you. Our database is large but far from complete. Please fill out the form below and we will be sure to include you in our database. In turn, we will add your business to our live feed and share this database with our partner websites who will list your products and services in their business directories.  ','Chamber of Commerce','We are helping to build the bitcoin chamber of commerce by providing our database of bitcoin businesses to the public