 ,(88,' The BTC Pulse was out first plugin. It&nbsp;creates a live stream out of bitcoin conversations in the community. It can easily be embedded into your webpage using a single line of javascript code. Below is a demo.  \r\n Iframes are not supported by your browser, so nothing is displayed\r\n   \r\n To embed the plugin into your website or blog add the following line of code where you want the plugin to appear. \r\n &lt;script type=&rdquo;text/javascript&rdquo; src=&rdquo;http://api.bitcoinbulletin.com/btcpulse&rdquo;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; \r\n If you decide to emebed the plugin beaware that development on the plugin has been halted due to a lack of interest, and that there are several known issues with the plugin. However, development will continue if the interest level picks back up. \r\n  The BTC Pulse plugin is used by a few websites. They are listed here.  The Bitcoin Bulletin: The Bitcoin Bulletin, our sister website, uses the BTC Economy extensively in their website. It can be found on almost every webpage.   Btc.IsNan.org: A bitcoin marketplace where you can write reviews about other merchants.  ','BTC Pulse Plugin','The BTC Pulse plugin creates a live stream out of bitcoin conversations in the community. It can easily be embedded into your webpage using a single line of javascript code.','/plugins/btc-pulse-plugin','2011-07-11 19:45:00','2011-10-03 10:59:15',NULL)
 ,(89,' BTC Economy Wiki  We also have a Wiki page on the BTC Economy plugin. Numerous websites across the bitcoin community use the BTC Economy plugin. Here is a list of websites known to support the plugin.  Generalize Website: \r\n Embedding the plugin is easy - just copy and paste the following line of code where you want the plugin to appear. \r\n &nbsp; \r\n&lt;script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://api.searchbitcoin.com/btceconomy\"&gt;&lt;/script&gt; \r\n &nbsp; \r\n The plugin will automatically attempt to resize itself to fit into the space it is given. Feel free to contact us if you have any troubles. We will be happy to help resolve any issues you may encounter, or to help step you through the process.  \r\n \r\n \r\n &nbsp;   The BTC Economy plugin creates a live feed out of bitcoin merchandise and services that have been found using our search engine. The plugin can be easily embedded into almost any webpage or blog. Click on the instructions tab to install the plugin into the following systems. \r\n &nbsp; \r\n\r\n\r\nBlogger / Blogspot&nbsp;(Instructions)\r\nGeneral Webpage (Instructions)\r\n\r\n   Blogger / Blogspot: \r\n A special gadget has been written for adding the BTC Economy to Blogger and Blogspot pages. To embed the gadget login to your blog follow these steps.&nbsp; \r\n   \r\n\r\nSign-in to your page and click \"Design\".\r\nClick \"Add a Gadget\" where you want to add the BTC Economy.\r\nIn the pop-up click \"Add you own\".\r\nAdd the following URL into the text box, click submit and save. \r\n \r\nhttp://www.api.searchbitcoin.com/apps/btceconomy/hooks/blogspot.xml \r\n&nbsp;  \r\n abelsfire.com \r\n bitbrew.net \r\n bitcoinbabe.com \r\n bitcoinbulletin.com \r\n bitcoincyberstore.com \r\n bitcoinforbeginners.blogspot.com \r\n bitcoinme.com \r\n bitcoinproject.net \r\n bitfreak.info \r\n bitstarter.co \r\n bitvapes.com \r\n bitucopia.com \r\n btcxc.info \r\n divare.dyndns-web.com \r\n hotac.org \r\n jsclosurejunkie.blogspot.com \r\n kosites.com \r\n owlick.blogspot.com \r\n pakhomov.org \r\n rjsteinert.com \r\n searchbitcoin.com \r\n searchbitcoin.tumblr.com \r\n spreadbitcoins.com \r\n thebitcoin.blogspot.com \r\n tiptopgem.com \r\n twpg.blogspot.com \r\n tradersedgedice.com \r\n weusecoins.com (through API) \r\n ','BTC Economy Plugin','The BTC Economy plugin creates a live feed out of bitcoin merchandise and services that have been found using our search engine. The plugin has been extremely successful, and runs on numerous websites across the bitcoin community.','/plugins/btc-economy-plugin','2011-07-11 20:23:00','2011-10-03 10:59:15',NULL)
