 ,(96,'Start accepting bitcoin payments in just 5 minutes. Here is how.  * Your first bitcoin customers will probably be eager to guide you through your first transactions. But as is always the case, be wary of scams.   After submitting your website, consider adding the BTC Economy Feed to your webage to support the bitcoin economy.    \r\n Search Bitcoin helps people find merchandise and services available in the bitcoin community. The tools that we offer may be found in numerous popular websites such as weusecoins.com,&nbsp;bitcoinme.com, and many others. \r\n &nbsp; \r\n Adding your website to our database is easy and free, and your merchandise or service will receive free promotion in&nbsp;Search Bitcoin and in all the websites using our services. So what are you waiting for?  \r\n\r\n  \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n 1:&nbsp; \r\n\r\n\r\n Add a new page to your website for receiving traffic from the bitcoin community. \r\n &nbsp; \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n 2:&nbsp; \r\n\r\n\r\n Click to download one of these free logos for your bitcoin page. \r\n  \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n 3:&nbsp; \r\n\r\n\r\n Download and install the bitcoin software to get your fist bitcoin address. \r\n &nbsp; \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n 4:&nbsp; \r\n\r\n\r\n Add your bitcoin address underneath the logo along with a way to contact you.* \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n // \r\nADD WEBSITE \r\n ','Add Your Webpage','Add your website to our search engine. There are no fees, and your bitcoin site will be promoted through all of channels.','/vendors','2011-07-14 15:20:00','2011-10-03 10:59:15',NULL)
