 ,(123,' Bitcoin has done well in the past because of its novelty. Spectators excited about the worlds first decentralized digital currency eagerly entered into the market, and by doing so drove up the value of the currency. But now the rush appears to have ended. \r\n &nbsp; \r\n  \r\n &nbsp; \r\n In order for bitcoin to continue growing, the bitcoin community will have to find new uses for the currency. Bitcoin holders may no longer be able to rely on speculation to keep the price of their money high. New, alternative sources of activity that will attract people to the currency are now required. \r\n  Thus, the bitcoin community may need to focus additional attention and resources to encourage greater use of bitcoin in e-commerce. This is already starting to happen. Just in the past few months, several large online bitcoin stores opened their doors for business. But this is just a start. More bitcoin businesses are needed, and these businesses will need the support of the community to remain financially afloat. \r\n  Bitcoins have great potential. But innovation is required to realize the dream of a truly decentralized, Internet based currency. \r\n &nbsp; \r\n Visit our homepage to search our database of bitcoin products and services.  ','The Importance of Bitcoin Stores','In order for the value of bitcoin to remain steady, the bitcoin community will have to find new uses for the currency. Bitcoin holders may no longer be able to rely on speculation to keep the price of their money high. New, alternative sources of activity that will attract people to the currency are now required.','/blog/the-importance-of-bitcoin-stores','2011-09-04 19:19:00','2011-10-03 10:59:15',NULL)
 ,(125,'Compact Digital \r\nVideo Camera \r\n  Remote Controlled \r\nFormula Racing Car \r\n&nbsp; \r\n  Playstation 3 \r\n(temporarily sold out) \r\n&nbsp; \r\n   Search Bitcoin tracks how many times people click on merchandise in our live feed and search results. This allows us to determine the most popular merchandise offered in the bitcoin community, which are listed below. Drum-roll please! \r\n &nbsp;   &nbsp; \r\n Check out all the merchandise available from the many bitcoin stores - just visit our homepage to see all that the bitcoin community has to offer.  ','Most Sought After Bitcoin Merchandise','Search Bitcoin tracks how many times people click on merchandise in our live feed and search results. This has allowed us to determine the most popular merchandise offered in the bitcoin community, which are listed here.','/blog/most-sought-after-bitcoin-merchandise','2011-09-29 20:56:00','2011-10-03 10:59:15',NULL);

